Flavors of the World
Wherever we fly around the globe, we have the enviable job
of tasting and savouring the cuisines of the world. We invite
you to share our discoveries while traveling with us.
Entrees
POT ROAST JARDINIERE
Braised Slices of U.S. Choice Beef

BAKED LASAGNA
Our Version of the Classic Pasta from Southern Italy.
We Present a Hearty Meat Sauce and Ricotta Cheese
Nested between Layers of Lasagna Noodles, Topped with a
Delightful Blend of Mornay Sauce and Parmesan Cheese.
COLD CHICKEN PLATE
Tender Young Chicken Deep Fried to a Golden Brown
and Served with a Buffet Assortment of Deli Style
Potato Salad, Relishes, and Cottage Cheese with Fruit.
